lead_paragraph: It was a photo taken with Michael Phelps that inspired Joseph Schooling to Olympic gold. So when he was mobbed by fans on his return to Singapore, he made sure he posed for a few.

headline.main: The 'Golden Boy' Schooling Mobbed on Return to Singapore
